    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and slice your<strong> carrot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into discs on the diagonal</p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s]</strong> in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and chop into large chunks</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> mince</strong> to a large bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>mince mixture</strong></p><p>Divide the<strong> mince mixture</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and shape into 3 meatballs per person</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min on each side until browned</p><p>Once the meatballs have browned, transfer them to a plate and set aside, these will finish cooking in the sauce later (reserve the pan!)</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped leek</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the leek is cooking, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in 650ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.3L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>chicken stock</strong></p><p>Once the leek is soft, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chicken stock</strong>, <strong>spelt</strong> and <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for an initial 13 min</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>After an initial 13 min, add the <strong>sliced carrot</strong> and <strong>browned meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 12-15 min further or until the spelt is tender and the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>spring meatball & spelt stew</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>mint sauce </strong>to a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a small splash of <strong>cold water </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>minty drizzle</strong></p><p>Discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spring-minty-lamb-meatball-and-spelt-stew/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spring meatball & spelt stew</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>minty drizzle</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
